{"tid":1846735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署設施29號起暫停開放","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:44:07.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f305530f20a07fef21d9341786b278344a1a5bfe","tid":1846735,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封關未呀屌你老母林鄭</span></span>"},{"pid":"29a7ccc3b050d5d477bb71d9378240512935da9c","tid":1846735,"uid":250242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"[求下大家] 盡快立即三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1月28不封關 1月29不上班"},{"pid":"efbc277a140f911baf38653029cbefcd26365ee7","tid":1846735,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"古物古蹟辦事處和康樂及文化事務署宣布，為配合政府「對公共衞生有重要性的新型傳染病預備及應變計劃」下提升應變級別至緊急及避免市民聚集，轄下設施明日起關閉。<br />\n<br />\n古蹟辦關閉的設施包括，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港文物探知館、屏山鄧族文物館暨文物徑訪客中心、新田大夫第、沙田王屋村古屋、黃竹坑新圍十號、下白泥碉堡、大埔上碗窰村碗窰展覽、大嶼山東涌炮台展覽中心及西貢東龍洲炮台展覽中心</span>，直至另行通告。設施關閉期間，所有教育活動及公眾導賞服務暫停。<br />\n<br />\n康文署將由明日起，暫停開放多項設施，並取消在有關場地舉行的康樂、體育及文化活動，直至另行通告。暫停開放的陸上和水上運動設施包括，<span style=\"color: red;\">所有體育館、運動場、草地球場、人造草地足球場、網球場、壁球場、草地滾球場、高爾夫球設施、公眾游泳池、泳灘、屯門康樂體育中心、水上活動中心和度假營。文化設施則包括所有博物館、表演場地、公共圖書館及附設之自修室、流動圖書館，以及音樂事務處的音樂中心。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505164-20200128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505164-20200128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5q7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=aab4d9ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505164-20200128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a7795779\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505164-20200128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d1d12d51531e0aefe83b8260054b267519b1359b","tid":1846735,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;草地球場、人造草地足球場&quot;<br />\n呢D 要 book 場，得十幾廿人嘅室外活動都唔得? 都要封?<br />\n<br />\n冬天嘅 &quot;泳灘&quot; 呢D室外都封 ?<br />\n<br />\n但大家繼續要返工，逼爆狗鐵, 巴士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6b9470eab9a525c69e9dd39572e49e8c72fe07","tid":1846735,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"連運運都唔比做(雖然有都唔做)點提升抵抗力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n古蹟辦果d 一日都唔知有冇500人次 (九龍公園裡面果個經過都唔會行入去)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5bdb759d2b4eee2651b1357ca35c76fc2f0095","tid":1846735,"uid":178568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"班dse慘過撚 圖書館 乜乜春春都冇"},{"pid":"8d7fa701ecfe64a8998321cdd210158de0b527ad","tid":1846735,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"買撚咗月票但就係因為垃圾政府政策ON99而浪費咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}